&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE CONTENT WRITING SPECIALIST ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WIN is looking for a Content Writing Specialist to join our growing team in India. We are looking for someone who can create clear, engaging, and high-impact content across digital platforms while understanding how modern AI tools can accelerate content creation, research, and ideation workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires a strong understanding of writing for US-based product companies, the ability to simplify complex ideas into compelling narratives, and a deep curiosity for new-age AI-assisted content workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
