&lt;li&gt;Conduct content research, competitor analysis, and trend tracking to improve content effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize content for engagement, readability, and SEO best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously experiment with modern content formats, storytelling approaches, and AI-assisted workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple content projects while maintaining quality and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
