&lt;p data-start=&quot;3454&quot; data-end=&quot;3743&quot;&gt;This position is part of a full-stack in-house marketing team that includes experts in SEO, paid media, design, and analytics. With that support, you’ll be able to adapt quickly, experiment more often, and expand your own skills while directly contributing to lead generation. 🔑&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do 📈&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1352&quot; data-end=&quot;1436&quot;&gt;Design, build, and optimize email marketing campaigns that engage and convert.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1439&quot; data-end=&quot;1528&quot;&gt;Develop landing pages and web content that resonate with prospects and drive leads.&lt;/li&gt;
