&lt;p data-start=&quot;3936&quot; data-end=&quot;4281&quot;&gt;We’re hiring a Performance Marketing Specialist to create and optimize campaigns that deliver measurable results. 📈 This role is focused on high-conversion email campaigns, landing pages, and digital content to drive franchisee and client acquisition. Perfect for someone who takes pride in seeing their work directly move the needle.&lt;/p&gt;
