&lt;li data-start=&quot;1744&quot; data-end=&quot;1855&quot;&gt;Apply best practices in copywriting, digital engagement, and conversion optimization to maximize results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1858&quot; data-end=&quot;1954&quot;&gt;Stay on top of digital marketing trends and competitor strategies, bringing new ideas forward.&lt;/li&gt;
