&lt;li&gt;Operate in an agile environment to develop functional and technical design specifications, project plans, use cases, data migration plans, wireframes, and workflow diagrams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a liaison between business and tech teams to convert requirements into digital products for web, mobile, apps and VR.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate ability to think strategically about business, product, and technical architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support design, development, testing and rollout of digital products and applications.&lt;/li&gt;
