&lt;li&gt;Bachelors degree in engineering or computer science&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly analytical with expertise in gathering, analyzing and documenting requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent knowledge of Agile Scrum methodologies including JIRA, Confluence or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong fundamentals in application development, data modeling, ETL, and BI tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Like to work hard, have fun, laugh with colleagues, and embrace accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE OFFER :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly inclusive and collaborative culture built on mutual respect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on core values, initiative, leadership and adaptability&lt;/li&gt;
