&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE PROJECT MANAGER ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WIN is looking for a proactive and execution-focused Project Manager who can drive projects end-to-end, remove blockers quickly, manage timelines efficiently, and ensure strong collaboration across teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who can lead from the front, a structured thinker who understands&amp;nbsp;technology well enough to hold teams accountable, provide meaningful feedback, and ensure&amp;nbsp;smooth execution without unnecessary process overhead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organize and manage end-to-end execution of multiple SaaS-based projects and&amp;nbsp;priorities with strong ownership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define project scope, timelines, deliverables, dependencies, and responsibilities across&amp;nbsp;teams.&lt;/li&gt;
