&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE QA ENGINEER ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WIN is a leading proptech company, and we&#39;re looking for a detail-oriented QA Engineer to help deliver high-quality software experiences across our mobile and web platforms. In this role, you&#39;ll play a critical part in ensuring product reliability by testing end-to-end user journeys, identifying defects, and collaborating closely with cross-functional teams to improve product quality. If you&#39;re passionate about testing, automation, and building exceptional user experiences, we&#39;d love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test end-to-end user flows across web and mobile applications to ensure seamless user experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validate key product features including forms, media uploads, offline synchronization, and report generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, write, execute, and maintain manual and automated test cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform API testing using tools such as Postman to validate functionality, reliability, and performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, document, track, and verify defects using JIRA and other testing tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Product, Engineering, and Design teams throughout the development lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in sprint planning, requirement reviews, and release validation activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to continuous improvement of QA processes, testing frameworks, and quality standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIRED QUALIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience in software quality assurance, including both manual and automation testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with automation testing tools such as Selenium, Cypress, Appium, or similar frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of web, mobile, and SaaS application testing methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience performing API testing using Postman or similar tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in creating and executing test plans, test cases, and bug reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong debugging, analytical, and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in Agile/Scrum development environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and collaboration skills with cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
